snippet.title: Pararomantic Trailer [KESÄPELIOPINNOT 2022]
snippet.description:
Pararomantic is a blood chilling dating-simulator visual-novel made in Unreal Engine as part of university course in game making. 

You can download the game for free from our Itch-page here:
https://vabajaba.itch.io/pararomantic

Music by Ross Budgen: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zuw_O5MU5CE
